  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2024-05-14",
    "date": "2024-08-07T14:06:14Z",
    "text": "Debt Per Taxpayer Information Act\u00a0\n\nThis bill requires the President's budget submission and the concurrent budget resolution to provide an estimate of the pro rata amount for each taxpayer of the public debt. It also requires information relating to\u00a0federal government revenue, outlays, and deficit and related information to be included on a taxpayers's W-2 form.\u00a0\n\n\u00a0\n\n\u00a0"
  },
